<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PersonNote/23> rdfs:label "Person Note: #23" ;
	a dprr:PersonNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "A friend of Catullus who saw service in Hisp. Cit. (Catull. 9.5ff.; 12.14ff.), and also under a Piso, probably Caesoninus, Cos. 58 and Procos. in Macedonia in 57-55 (28; 47). See Syme, Historia 5, 1956, 211ff.-RP 1.323; Class. et Mediaevalia 17, 1956, 129-134-RP 1.300-304. No evidence that either he or Catullus was an officer or magistrate." .
